{"tid":901572,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我到今日先發現 利孝和夫人 並唔係叫利孝和","createTime":"2018-11-14T06:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T23:52:02.000Z","uid":111957,"like":294,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"f619aac12230d3e9377c2805d0c0bc2681fea23d","tid":901572,"uid":111957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"係咪得我自己一個咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba487746b8f2a6c9a1c7787d2549ae8538169a3f","tid":901572,"uid":146435,"like":893,"dislike":5,"score":888,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"係兩個人黎on9 一個叫利孝和 一個叫夫人"},{"pid":"0278ae57e2bd7e80c719c37404a18a05b7b7ec2a","tid":901572,"uid":65371,"like":569,"dislike":9,"score":560,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"利孝和夫係一族人嚟，同內塔黎亞湖一鳩樣"},{"pid":"795313d23663eec769f5fb05a34362e2f904dc74","tid":901572,"uid":44243,"like":453,"dislike":9,"score":444,"quote":{"pid":"ba487746b8f2a6c9a1c7787d2549ae8538169a3f","tid":901572,"uid":146435,"like":893,"dislike":5,"score":888,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"係兩個人黎on9 一個叫利孝和 一個叫夫人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:40:13.000Z","msg":"利孝 和 夫人"},{"pid":"e42b41a6ae84e4ebba1b4780653470cb7a042ba2","tid":901572,"uid":107927,"like":42,"dislike":66,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"利孝和和利孝和夫人和利孝和和利孝和夫人所生的兒子利憲彬"},{"pid":"9da0f24609cd82d722371c61d3df2f9ea8e13116","tid":901572,"uid":48796,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"利孝 和 夫人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ab1b2ab1ddb5c5e268b589593e912390188bb","tid":901572,"uid":119173,"like":5,"dislike":114,"score":-109,"quote":{"pid":"0278ae57e2bd7e80c719c37404a18a05b7b7ec2a","tid":901572,"uid":65371,"like":569,"dislike":9,"score":560,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T06:39:43.0