/static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20131215/large/a0205a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20131215%2Flarge%2Fa0205a.gif&h=e4b08956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二次世界大戰結束後不久，香港大學女生宿位短缺。何東爵士為了紀念他於1943年逝世的原配夫人麥秀英女士，捐贈了一百萬元予香港大學興建女子宿舍，並將之命名為何東夫人紀念堂。(wiki)<br />\n<br />\n何東同麥秀英後來合葬於快活谷（跑馬地）香港墳場<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/ab/HK_Cemetery_Sir_Robert_Ho_Tung_KBE_with_wife.JPG/1024px-HK_Cemetery_Sir_Robert_Ho_Tung_KBE_with_wife.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fab%2FHK_Cemetery_Sir_Robert_Ho_Tung_KBE_with_wife.JPG%2F1024px-HK_Cemetery_Sir_Robert_Ho_Tung_KBE_with_wife.JPG&h=c88cb271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n==<br />\n另外，何東平妻（第二任老婆；當年重係一夫多妻制）張蓮覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8d/LadyHotung.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F8d%2FLadyHotung.jpg&h=795c13cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何東花園（Ho Tung Gardens）中文原名曉覺園，就係以張蓮覺命名<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20120121/large/21la1p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120121%2Flarge%2F21la1p2a.jpg&h=8d9346ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑馬地山光道佛寺<strong>東蓮覺苑</strong>就係用何<strong>東</strong>同張<strong>蓮覺</strong>合名<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/34/HK_TungLinKokYuen.JPG/1024px-HK_TungLinKokYuen.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F3%2F34%2FHK_TungLinKokYuen.JPG%2F1024px-HK_TungLinKokYuen.JPG&h=8cf60183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1931年何東送贈二太太張靜蓉（法號張蓮覺）10萬港元作為結婚周年禮物。篤信佛教的張靜蓉在早一年於波斯富街為當時家貧女子而設立第一所佛教學校「寶覺第一義學」，並在1932年秋迎請鎮江竹林寺住持靄亭法師於新界青山成立「寶覺佛學研究社」以培育宏法女性專門人才。翌年張靜蓉得譚煥堂幫助以1.7萬元向政府投得香港跑馬地山光道一塊面積1.2萬平方呎的地皮，並將整筆結婚周年贈款用於興建東蓮覺苑及寶覺小學，直至1935年5月工程完成，前設於波斯富街的女子義學及青山之佛學社相繼遷入，入口山門的石柱分別為「寶覺義學校」與「寶覺佛學社」的刻石，述說了東蓮覺苑前身的歷史。<br />\n<br />\n2009年，東蓮覺苑獲獲古物古蹟辦事處評級為香港一級歷史建築。<br />\n2015年，東蓮覺苑將會耗資約億港元以進行大規模的全苑翻新工程，為期達5至10年，期間繼續對外開放。<br />\n2017年6月8日，東蓮覺苑獲古物諮詢委員會確認為法定古蹟。<br />\n(wiki)<br />\n==<br />\n有篇文介紹張蓮覺，好詳細：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.buddhismmiufa.org.hk/buddhism/people/cheunglinkwok.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.buddhismmiufa.org.hk%2Fbuddhism%2Fpeople%2Fcheunglinkwok.htm&d=NFFS3mC8m57zLGIwnaKavU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=adbee82b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.buddhismmiufa.org.hk/buddhism/people/cheunglinkwok.htm</a>"},{"pid":"40caf58bbd0162060605d166997e369f76d71b94","tid":901572,"uid":106326,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"依家啲後生其實要保衛粵語應該真係搵返個百幾集出黎傳道<br />\n<br />\n奈何已經因爲generation gap <br />\n無人再識笑了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36eb86686298a137ad0182f516100725574a060","tid":901572,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"尒巧喔`夫人"},{"pid":"afa98a1a4bdc4d489f16cfee701009043e1fd9b8","tid":901572,"uid":134421,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"從來冇人教呢手d香港歷史"},{"pid":"59ee0dd3ff9d09287de4f9d5e0aeb13aad786a13","tid":901572,"uid":147219,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:37:07.000Z","msg":"關我蛋治事啊？"},{"pid":"71a4322fe140ef19518197f6423db0d8b050afba","tid":901572,"uid":147219,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"關我食三文治啊？"},{"pid":"8655e24f2c1e9c8abd465ff0d44fe3b0c2c0c1cd","tid":901572,"uid":11153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"等我拆穿你個西洋鏡啦！"},{"pid":"30b9fa2c6c9c87bbbb8048a4663a9a0f8058c9b0","tid":901572,"uid":57854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor